### `apps/dashboard/src/lib/auth.ts` (FULLY IMPLEMENTED -- no changes needed)

Provides all session management functions:
- `createSession(session: Session)` -- signs a JWT with `{ userId, githubLogin, githubId }`, 7-day expiry
- `getSession()` -- reads cookie, verifies JWT, returns `Session | null`
- `setSessionCookie(token)` -- sets HTTP-only, Secure, SameSite=Lax cookie named `gblockparty-session`
- `clearSessionCookie()` -- deletes the session cookie

The `Session` interface:
```typescript
interface Session {
  userId: string;
  githubLogin: string;
  githubId: number;
}
```

